data.description: Discover the perfect canvas for your waterfront dreams in the prestigious Loch Haven neighborhood. Nestled just across the street from the tranquil waters and a stone's throw away from the homeowner's community marina, this stunning, cleared lot beckons with promise. This immaculate parcel of land is gracefully poised between two charming homes with dual street access from the front and back of the lot, offering a golden opportunity for both savvy investors and those seeking to craft their own sanctuary. Loch Haven is not just a neighborhood; it's a lifestyle. Residents are privileged with access to an array of exceptional amenities, including a welcoming homeowner's community marina, a serene sandy beach for relaxation, a tot lot for the little ones, and courts for basketball, volleyball, and tennis enthusiasts. This is a place where the joys of outdoor living come to life. Convenience is key, with a prime location that places you close to shopping, dining, the vibrant heart of Downtown Annapolis, and easy access to the bustling cities of DC, VA, and Baltimore. Every day offers a new adventure, whether it's exploring historic Annapolis or embarking on a waterfront voyage. Seize this incredible opportunity to embrace the water-inspired lifestyle you've always dreamed of, and secure one of the last available lots in this highly sought-after neighborhood. Time is of the essence, so don't let this chance to create your own waterfront haven slip away.
